# migrated from tests/cases/facts.chat (gen346).
# HERMETIC context via !set: empty base (no curated man(socrates)) and no world
# facts — so the teach-then-query assertions are genuine, not KB recall.
[mock hermetic]
!set PARROT0_BASE=
!set PARROT0_SESSION=
!set PARROT0_WORLD_FACTS=0
!set PARROT0_LANG=en

[test facts]
> is socrates a man?
< I don't know about man.
> socrates is a man
< Learned: man(socrates).
> is socrates a man?
< Yes.
> bob is an animal
< Learned: animal(bob).
> is bob an animal?
< Yes.
> is bob a man?
< No.
> is socrates an animal?
< No.
> hello
< Hi there!
> the quick brown fox
< I don't understand that yet.
